===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Allister (Masters)}}
Allister forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Gengar}} and {{form|Pumkaboo and Gourgeist|Super Size}} {{p|Gourgeist}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Gengar is capable of [[Gigantamax]]ing. Allister became a playable sync pair on October 22, 2021.

Allister has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. 

